 Requirements
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Proper Reason
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 -Both updates of Skidrow are missing important files for the Grand Campaign,
  without them the game is crashing in campaign mode.
 -Skidrow updates arent compatible with any prior Razor updates or
  Razor's DVD release. (Sound bug,old lua scripts and etc.)
 
 Install Notes
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 1. Extract RARs
 2. Copy the rzr-et8h.exe in your install folder and execute it
 3. Copy crack
 4. Have Fun!
